The Electron · node ATM · ATM · A fundamental lepton — no known size or structure, a true point particle that behaves as a quantum wave. It is NOT a tiny ball on a track; it exists as a smeared probability cloud around the nucleus.

universe of origin : ATM · The Atom
seal               : DOES ALL OF CHEMISTRY. The outer electrons form bonds, carry electricity, emit and absorb light, and set the atom's size and shape. Everything you touch, every reaction, every colour — that's electrons rearranging.
